comment: Curry (DAL) does not intentionally kick the ball on the play.
Barnes (DAL) makes incidental contact with Butler (CHI) that does not affect his SQBR.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of CHI possession is confirmed.
Mejri (DAL) makes body contact with Butler (CHI) that affects his layup attempt.
Wade (CHI) spins away from Williams (DAL) and the contact is marginal.
Curry (DAL) clamps the arm of Lopez (CHI) and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Lopez (CHI) makes contact with Nowitzki (DAL) that affects his SQBR.
Carter-Williams (CHI) sets the screen on Matthews (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Matthews (DAL) makes incidental contact with Butler (CHI) that does not affect his SQBR.
Williams (DAL) makes marginal contact with Wade (CHI) that does not affect his shot attempt.
